{"tid":318220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講真,點同屋企人親近d","createTime":"2017-07-12T02:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T05:58:38.000Z","uid":127864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"371a0c3a042f6906247f4b42b9fbaa439af45c47","tid":318220,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"畢左業幾年,做緊野<br />\n由細到大都唔知點解人地可以同老豆老母好friend咁<br />\n我就唔得,我同老豆都係一句起兩句止<br />\n知佢返工辛苦 六十幾歲都返工<br />\n其實我真係好想同佢地講：我愛你呀daddy 媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但男人老狗我又講唔出口,有冇巴絲都係咁<br />\n可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：21歲同老豆一齊做地盤佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好尊敬老豆"},{"pid":"16acecd699d86bfb890e1cce54b90b3d76078f06","tid":318220,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FViqNhuXgROc&d=tVQayoMpeeFv0KaNZAnvlm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a1977bd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc</a><br />\n<br />\n聽埋呢首歌真係好傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e30ab8600f0d8a0f70c2d265f2969ba393d9494","tid":318220,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要親近一早就親近左啦。"},{"pid":"866d9148f0edbc1225d61c148a3de50b6c8a964c","tid":318220,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大個左識諗 但無從入